        <p data-role="text">An&#xAD;i&#xAD;mal rights group Dobut&#xAD;sukikin says the dogs found crammed into the 30 sq m house house in Izumo city in western Ja&#xAD;pan were mostly mal&#xAD;nour&#xAD;ished or in&#xAD;fected with par&#xAD;a&#xAD;sites.</p>
